      <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
              <h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse5">Is this all there is?</a></h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <div class="panel-body">If you have created a profile and are already enjoying what we have put together, then you’ll be happy to know that this is just phase 1 of a larger scale project. What you see so far is a “first version” that’s meant to show health care decision makers, doctors, and funders the potential power of what it means to really design and develop tools for patients, based on what patients have told us they need. So, stick around, provide feedback, and watch us grow what you see today into what is possible tomorrow.</div>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading">
              <h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse6">Why should I create a profile?</a></h4>
          </div>
          <div id="collapse6" class="panel-collapse collapse">
              <div class="panel-body">If you haven’t created a profile yet or are just exploring this site to see what it’s about, then there’s a wealth of resources that we’ve pulled together to help you on your chronic care journey. But there’s so much more once you create a profile. With a login/profile, you get access to a wealth of tools that are personalized to your needs and situation that are only possible with some information from you.</div>
          </div>
